data.description: Bring us an offer! Charming 3/2 in a quiet neighborhood located in Comfort Texas! This home has 1400+/- sqft on .28 acres! No HOA and no city taxes with a lovely small town community. The kitchen and living area has tons of space for entertaining as well as a wood burning fireplace. Two of the three bedrooms have new flooring and trim work. The whole house has been painted inside and out to provide a modern canvas for the new owners. The backyard is spacious with plenty of room for parties and other events. The one car garage is oversized with tons of storage room and laundry area. Don't miss your opportunity to live in Comfort!
